<h3><img src="http://www.davidfriedmanphoto.com/blog/images/sidebar-about.png" alt="ABOUT" /></h3>
<p class="text">I'm <a href="http://www.davidfriedmanphoto.com">David Friedman</a>, a photographer based in New York City. This blog is a place for me to write about projects I'm working on, and things that inspire me. Be sure to check out <a href="http://www.davidfriedmanphoto.com">my portfolio</a> and when you're done you can visit my other blog, <a href="http://www.ironicsans.com">Ironic Sans</a>, to see what I come up with when I'm not taking pictures.</p>
